create package json
1. npm init -y

install web pack
2. 
npm install webpack --save-dev
esvel npm i webpack --save-dev
3.
npm i webpack-cli --save-dev     "webpack-cli": "^3.3.10", aldaa garaad bhaar ni ene huvilbar suulgasan
 4.
create webpack configuration file
webpack.config.js

const path = require('path');

module.exports = {
  entry: './src/index.js',
  output: {
    filename: 'main.js',
    path: path.resolve(__dirname, 'dist'),
  },
}; webpackiin sitaas huulav
5. html wep plagin ashiglay
npmjs.com s haigaarai html-webpack-plagin ined=x html deer automataar neriig bichij, js filuudiig index dotroo zooj dist dotor uusgej ogno

npm i --save-dev html-webpack-plugin
template gedgiig ni ashiglii
6.  install webpack dev server
npm i webpack-dev-server
7 babel saitaas ni suulga
npm install --save @babel/polyfill ene ni bur bolomjguig ni browser deer bichij ogdog uchir codetegee yana geed ene moduliig defendency ruu suulgana gesen 
babel loader suulga auto convert hiinenpm

git remote -v
git init
git remote add origin https://github.com/khishig25/recipe.git


npm install gevel packege jsonoosoo node_modulia uusgechihdeg. tiimees nod_modeliig damjuulah hadgalah shaardlagagui
